        "message": "Patch Set 9:\n\n> One other thought, same thing that Controller is independent now.  \n > Topic could be an independent entity as well provisioned on its\n > own.   This will allow stand up a pristine PDP-D, and go through,\n > controller, topic, and native policies to be configured with a work\n > load.\n\nHere, there will be authentication information, host addresses needed that probably is not desirable to be placed here, unless there is some sort of super-admin role putting together this, but thought to bring it up.",
