        "timestamp": "2019-11-21 18:16:55.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 10:\n\nSo if you update the controller policy, eg new version, then you have to find all policies that reference it and update them also so they point to the latest (same) version?",
        "patchset_number": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "cdda625b14371f3a87c8222ff4d4ede1487ac57f",
