        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-11-21 18:47:34.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 10:\n\nI am more concerned about if PDP-D can support multiple versioned controllers with the same controllerName. Maybe we can put a restriction here to make PDP-D always run the latest version of different controllers. It is simpler to support in Frankfurt.",
        "patchset_number": 10
      },
